biosynthesis from histidine via gamma-glutamyl-hercynylcysteine sulfoxide\tFalse\tPMID:20420449\tIDA\t\tUniProt\tinfores:go\t\t\t\t\t\t{}\r\nUniProtKB:O69671\tbiolink:related_to\tGO:0052704\tegtB\tNone\tergothioneine biosynthesis from histidine via gamma-glutamyl-hercynylcysteine sulfoxide\tFalse\tGO_REF:0000024\tISS\t\tUniProt\tinfores:go\t\t\t\t\t\t{}\r\nUniProtKB:O69670\tbiolink:related_to\tGO:0052704\tegtC\tNone\tergothioneine biosynthesis from histidine via gamma-glutamyl-hercynylcysteine sulfoxide\tFalse\tGO_REF:0000024\tISS\t\tUniProt\tinfores:go\t\t\t\t\t\t{}\r\nUniProtKB:O69668\tbiolink:related_to\tGO:0052704\tegtE\tNone\tergothioneine biosynthesis from histidine via gamma-glutamyl-hercynylcysteine sulfoxide\tFalse\tGO_REF:0000024\tISS\t\tUniProt\tinfores:go\t\t\t\t\t\t{}\r\n","exit":0,"description":"List direct annotations for GO 0052704","truncated":false},"title":"List direct annotations for GO 0052704","time":{"start":1778984092582,"end":1778984093148}},"id":"prt_e33b6e9ab0019iU6dZVvze61z1","sessionID":"ses_1cc49cb2affepFEBRfr82gW1Mc","messageID":"msg_e33b6c093001NCz1zk5lk9q3PO"}}
